Author: dukeleto#7326
Content: "copy as curl" from Chrome is an easy way to OC your z9m

Author: dukeleto#7326
Content: look at your Network requests inspector tab, press "save and apply" with default (no OC settings), then "copy as curl" and change 500 to the freq you want

Author: dukeleto#7326
Content: then you have a CLI command to run to change freq, better than inspect element every time 😃
